name: All Wrapped Up
Lore: 'A capture cable is a quick and effective way for bounty hunters to suddenly snare their target.',
Text: 'Deploy on your side of table. We Have A Prisoner and Oo-ta Goo-ta Solo? play for free and are immune to Sense. Also, whenever opponent forfeits a character, your bounty hunter present may capture that character. (Immune to Alter.)',
